 hence the growth of planetesimals. The new parameter\nset might possibly lead to an enhanced sticking as more energy can be stored in\nthe system before breakup.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Mar 2012 08:20:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-01-17"}
